text: Noticed this nice cafe near my neighbourhood and finally went there for their breakfast for two promo with my wife. For just $10, each of us have a nice fluffy sandwich with ham and a nice cup of latte. We enjoyed our breakfast very much. The staffs there are very pleasant and the atmosphere is joyful despite being busy during the morning peak hours. Will visit again ðŸ˜Š
